---
---
<section class="py-24 bg-navy-900 text-white relative overflow-hidden">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 relative z-10">
    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-end mb-16 gap-6">
      <div class="max-w-2xl">
        <p class="text-gold-400 font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-sm mb-3">Our Process</p>
        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold mb-6">How We Work</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-300 text-lg">A streamlined, transparent process from initial concept to final delivery, ensuring quality at every step.</p>
      </div>
      <a href="/contact-us/" class="bg-gold-400 text-navy-900 hover:bg-gold-500 px-8 py-3.5 rounded-full font-bold text-sm transition-all uppercase tracking-wide whitespace-nowrap">
        NEED HELP
      </a>
    </div>
    
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8 lg:gap-12 relative">
      <!-- Connecting Line -->
      <div class="hidden lg:block absolute top-12 left-[12.5%] right-[12.5%] h-0.5 bg-white/20 z-0"></div>
      
      <div class="relative z-10 text-center">
        <div class="w-24 h-24 mx-auto bg-white rounded-full p-5 shadow-xl mb-6 flex items-center justify-center border-4 border-navy-900 group hover:border-gold-400 transition-colors">
          <img src="/images/process/Step-1-1.png" alt="Consultation" class="w-full h-full object-contain" />
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">1. Consultation</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">We listen to your needs, discuss materials, and align on your brand vision.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="relative z-10 text-center">
        <div class="w-24 h-24 mx-auto bg-white rounded-full p-5 shadow-xl mb-6 flex items-center justify-center border-4 border-navy-900 group hover:border-gold-400 transition-colors">
          <img src="/images/process/Step-2-1.png" alt="Concept" class="w-full h-full object-contain" />
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">2. Concept & Design</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">Creating 3D mockups and refining designs before sample production.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="relative z-10 text-center">
        <div class="w-24 h-24 mx-auto bg-white rounded-full p-5 shadow-xl mb-6 flex items-center justify-center border-4 border-navy-900 group hover:border-gold-400 transition-colors">
          <img src="/images/process/MG_8933-2.png" alt="Production" class="w-full h-full object-cover rounded-full" />
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">3. Production</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">Strict quality control during the bulk manufacturing process.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="relative z-10 text-center">
        <div class="w-24 h-24 mx-auto bg-white rounded-full p-5 shadow-xl mb-6 flex items-center justify-center border-4 border-navy-900 group hover:border-gold-400 transition-colors">
          <img src="/images/process/MG_8942.png" alt="Delivery" class="w-full h-full object-cover rounded-full" />
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">4. Final Result</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">Delivery of high-quality sportswear directly to your warehouse.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
